uthern California\", \"from\": 3630, \"to\": 3649}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I always thought if I can get to L.A., that would definitely be a special moment for me, because that's kind of where it all started, when I went off to (USC),\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3671, \"to\": 3841, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3705, \"end\": 3709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999946285243, \"rank\": 3.655113674582091e-09, \"text\": \"L.A.\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 3826, \"end\": 3829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USC_Trojans\", \"score\": 0.9997839379501267, \"rank\": 0.0002158232731780044, \"text\": \"USC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USC_Trojans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USC_Trojans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a special moment\", \"from\": 3736, \"to\": 3752}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If I can go longer, even better, but that's the plan, to try to make it to at least to LA.\", \"from\": 3843, \"to\": 3934, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the plan\", \"from\": 3888, \"to\": 3896}, {\"ngram\": \"LA\", \"from\": 3931, \"to\": 3933}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The moment I stop having fun with it then, yeah, I will be done with it,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 3936, \"to\": 4020, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 3962, \"to\": 3965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But if I am still having fun and enjoying it and having a great passion for it, I am going to keep going.\\\"\", \"from\": 4021, \"to\": 4128, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 4047, \"to\": 4050}, {\"ngram\": \"a great passion\", \"from\": 4078, \"to\": 4093}]}, {\"sentence\": \"REUTERS Olympics Los Angeles E-paper Newsletters Podcasts RSS Feed About Us Terms & Conditi